, \"from\": 242, \"to\": 252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can not be true.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yesterday, 2 hours after writing 'I deserve it' on social media, I felt a sharp pain in my side.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"a sharp pain\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"my side\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emergency room, CT scan, ultrasound, blood tests....\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CT_scan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.504895036683133e-16, \"text\": \"CT scan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CT_scan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CT_scan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Emergency room\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"blood tests\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Probable kidney stone.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Probable kidney stone\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now I find myself, 3 days before the competition I sacrificed everything for, lying in a bed, helpless, with a fever of 38.8\\u00bb.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"a bed\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"a fever\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"38.8\\u00bb\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Tamberi has no intention of giving up and will go to France anyway: \\u00abI was supposed to leave for Paris today and start my journey towards this great dream, but I was advised to postpone the flight to tomorrow, hoping that with some rest, this nightmare will end.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999942445358, \"rank\": 5.7554647504027324e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tamberi\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"no intention\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"France\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"this great dream\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"the flight\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"tomorrow\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"some rest\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"this nightmare\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All I can do now is wait and pray\\u00bb.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00bb\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by HALFSHAVE (@gianmarcotamberi) Gimbo's conclusion is bitter but also full of hope: \\u00abI do not deserve all this, I did everything for this Olympics, everything.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A post\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"HALFSHAVE (@gianmarcotamberi) Gimbo's conclusion\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympics\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really do not deserve it.One thing is certain, I do not know how I will get there, but I will be on that track and I will give my soul until the last jump, whatever my condition will be.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"